{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1776117073.186478", "card_id": "Q_2026654782224430095", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "90 后女子后背疼，含硝酸甘油舌下片并开车 9 分钟去急诊，确诊心梗，这些自救行为哪些正确，哪些还能更稳妥？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "【#90 后女子后背疼 9 分钟完成心梗自救#】#心梗发作前的主要症状#警惕！后背这种疼可能是心梗！近日，一名 90 后女子早上 8 点多感觉左侧后背传来一阵痉挛痛，起初以为是劳累没有休息好导致的岔气，没太在意，然而躺床上休息时后背依然疼，女子就含了家里的硝酸甘油舌下片，稍微缓解了一些，立马觉得不对劲了，就自己开车去医院急诊，路途用了 9 分钟，中间又含了一次，到医院检查后被确诊为心梗，而她整个自救过程也为医生抢救赢得了宝贵时间。医生提醒：心梗前兆易混淆，如感觉胸痛胸闷、呼吸困难、后背痛、莫名牙疼，一定要及时就医。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8cd7a6c7d0e4fcddf2cf300f4009c3d6.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "314 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2026654782224430095"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4pq01r+qs4liEAMaCTExOTExNDI0NiC53uzOBjAAOJMCQAByEzIwMjY2NTQ3ODIyMjQ0MzAwOTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1776117073.187556", "card_id": "Q_2026223211436676545", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待有人通过豆包买保险，结果豆包编造订单，受害人支付的却是个人二维码，还被立案了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有人在豆包上咨询保险，结果豆包像模像样的生成订单号，结果用户支付扫码支付 1600 多元，后发现查询不到保险订单号，报警了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2baa1dfe42dcec3331ad78f6c86a8112_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "197 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2026223211436676545"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4pq01r+qs4liEAMaCTExOTA5OTQ5NyDLuubOBjAAOGxAAXITMjAyNjIyMzIxMTQzNjY3NjU0NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1776117073.188020", "card_id": "Q_2026808990546306928", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 98}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待大司马直播吐槽卡普空「不仅不给赞助还要收钱」，并对比蓝洞（PUBG）的大力赞助？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "从商业和版权角度看，卡普空的做法真的「有问题」吗？ 近日大司马在直播中聊到《街霸 6》时，表示该游戏很有看点，但吐槽卡普空的商业逻辑太搞了。 他表示想要把赛事或活动搞大，卡普空不仅不给赞助，反而会因为 IP 侵权找主办方收钱，甚至可能起诉。 之后他对比了蓝洞（PUBG），表示蓝洞不仅允许举办活动，后期还提供资金和大力赞助。 大司马在直播中表达了不解：自己帮游戏带流量，厂商却因为版权问题要收钱。他认为：「我出人出钱帮游戏搞大声音，你别找我要钱啊。」 到底是「厂商该给主播广告费」，还是「主播办赛该给厂商买授权」？这种逻辑冲突反映了当前国内电竞直播行业怎样的现状？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-73a0e301a8af80bccf1bb98575240ce2_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "178 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2026808990546306928"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4pq01r+qs4liEAMaCTExOTExOTU5OSDX/e7OBjAAOKEBQAJyEzIwMjY4MDg5OTA1NDYzMDY5Mjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1776117073.189291", "card_id": "Q_2016238306929696793", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么吕小军在退役一两年后肌肉会掉那么多？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是否有 dy 的可能，纯好奇，因为按我的理解，顶级自然训练者用年限堆起来的肌肉根本没那么好掉"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e19665f08646afd368df99b4bfe511a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "142 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2016238306929696793"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4pq01r+qs4liEAMaCTExODc1MzgxNyCglNXNBjAAOF9AA3ITMjAxNjIzODMwNjk