六万条毒蛇年入百万，利润真能这么高吗？毒蛇都有哪些价值？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 10 日，广西桂林一位 95 年出生的秦女士大学毕业两年后回村，帮父亲一起养蛇，年入百万。目前，她养了 5 万多条五步蛇、将近 1 万条眼镜蛇。起初父亲不让自己接触这个行业，觉得养毒蛇危险性太高。后来父亲忙不过来，自己就回来帮忙。她说自己不怕蛇，出生前家里就在养蛇了。 广西 95 后女生返乡养蛇年入百万：目前养了 5 万多条五步蛇，近 1 万条眼镜蛇，「不怕蛇，出生前家里就养蛇了」_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ffa860a6a704655f5d7881ed44bcd1b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2026633813309092447"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4pq01r+qs4liEAMaCTExOTExMzYwOCCyt+zOBjAAONcBQBxyEzIwMjY2MzM4MTMzMDkwOTI0NDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1776117073.200535", "card_id": "Q_1992694701514564466", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我发现其实挺多单机游戏通关后是没有新增什么内容的，为什么还有大量玩家愿意二周目、三周目重复游玩？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-489d7f9a6ea0c17a9c3cf1b78699ef1e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1992694701514564466"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI4pq01r+qs4liEAMaCTExODAwMTYyMiDvxv7KBjAAODRAHXITMTk5MjY5NDcwMTUxNDU2NDQ2NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billbo